Introducing 889 Bushwick ave, a newly constructed luxury rental development in the heart of Bushwick. 

889 Bushwick ave is the first part of a 223-unit brand new construction project that will take over this entire block. At 889 we offer 56 Units with a choice of one, two or three bedroom apartments - most of which feature private outdoor spaces and state-of-the-art amenities.


Amenities of the unit: 
Central A/C 
Hardwood Floors 
Natural Light in Living Area 
Dishwasher 
Outdoor Space 
Stone countertops

Building amenities:
- Co-working library space with private niches
- Fully furnished and landscaped roof deck overlooking the one of a kind 
Manhattan skyline 
- Laundry in building 
- Bike storage 
- Fully equipped Gym 
- Game room 
- Common courtyard 
- Garage 

Surrounded by neighborhood amenities, galleries, restaurants, coffee shops & bars. 
This spot is 5 minutes walk to the JMZ at Gates Avenue... just a 30 minutes commute to SoHo, and 38 minutes to Midtown Manhattan.
